{"tid":2334684,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"梁卓偉：變種病毒株傳播力達七成半","createTime":"2020-12-21T10:18:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T11:21:49.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"648fa92137096a7c9f1c7380dc48431a43f7df71","tid":2334684,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T10:18:40.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】政府專家顧問香港大學醫學院院長梁卓偉指，根據團隊的數學模型推算，英國的變種新型冠狀病毒株傳播力達七成半，與英國當地的推算七成脗合，他指若新病毒株傳入香港，將大大推高病毒繁殖率，令疫情惡化。<br />\n<br />\n港大醫學院院長梁卓偉：「即時繁殖率是0.81，如果新病毒株可以傳入香港，而真正的傳播力有75%這麼強，或強於75%，將0.81乘1.75，是可以將即時繁殖率推高至1.42，意思是指當數值大於1，病毒會繁殖得更快以及不會受到控制。」<br />\n<br />\n他表示，目前未有本地個案顯示，患者體內有任何病毒基因突變，港大會將樣本再次進行基因排序，了解會否有英國當地的變種病毒株傳入本港，至於目前的疫苗對變種病毒株大打折扣。<br />\n<br />\n梁卓偉指，暫時未有數據顯示受變種病毒株感染的患者會出現嚴重病情，目前仍需更多資料分析。"},{"pid":"392b67b1b4f53832a8c78179d214e019eb0f5fe6","tid":2334684,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T10:18:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=417438\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D417438&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzKZg5fsFimH5gYFReGFrXmU%3D&h=3b435cae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D417438&h=e82f441a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=417438</a>"},{"pid":"a1993776ff77492b5342184e1c1669bcd5cb0441","tid":2334684,"uid":292362,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T10:23:58.000Z","msg":"唔死就得啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a823e8dd2895a7845804dea140bdcc43b4594f","tid":2334684,"uid":228143,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T10:26:02.000Z","msg":"又恐懼 我就話外星人來到香港後可以一下秒殺晒人類啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54814ea4083bde5f4580e7adb7849a5fb6f41b4d","tid":2334684,"uid":78519,"like":2,"disl